== Umusaruro mushya uteganijwe ==
Itsinda rya Madhvani rirateganya kongera umusaruro i Kabuye kugera kuri toni 55.000 buri mwaka. Iterambere ririmo ishoramari rishya rifite agaciro ka miliyoni 75 US $ (hafi miliyari 60). Harimo kubaka sitasiyo y'umuriro wa co-generation ifite ingufu za 12 megawatts (16,092 hp) n'ikigo gikora Ethanol gifite ubushobozi bwo gutanga  ethanol litiro milion 6 buri mwaka. Guverinoma yu Rwanda nitsinda rya Madhvani bakoze ibiganiro kugirango iyi gahunda igerweho.  Muri Kanama 2016, guverinoma yashyize umukono ku masezerano y’ubwumvikane n’abashoramari baturutse muri [[Morise|Maurice]], kugira ngo bashinge uruganda rushya rw’isukari mu [[Intara y’Iburasirazuba|Ntara y’Uburasirazuba]] bw’u Rwanda, bivugwa ko ruzatwara hagati ya miliyoni 250 na miliyoni 300 USD. ruzajya kuri  hafi  hegitari ibihumbi 8 . bazakora kandi n'uruganda rukora amashanyarazi rufite  megawatts 25 . Ubushobozi bwo kubyaza umusaruro iki kigo gishya buteganijwe kuri toni 100.000  buri mwaka. <ref name="Up">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true" id="CITEREFNtirenganya2016">Ntirenganya, Emmanuel (8 August 2016). [http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/202415/ "Mauritian investors to construct sugar factory in Eastern Province"]. ''[[The New Times (Rwanda)|New Times (Rwanda)]]''. Kigali<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">24 October</span> 2017</span>.</cite></ref>

